Terraform Backend Configuration for S3
Uncomment and configure this block in main.tf if you want to use S3 backend

terraform {
  backend "s3" {
    bucket         = "your-terraform-state-bucket"
    key            = "quiz-please-stats/terraform.tfstate"
    region         = "eu-central-1"
    encrypt        = true
  }
}

To use this backend:
1. Create an S3 bucket for Terraform state
3. Uncomment the backend block above
4. Update the values with your bucket name and region
5. Run: terraform init -migrate-state
